'''Paradox Drive''' (Japanese: '''進撃パラドックス''' ''Advancing Paradox'') is the seventh {{TCGP|B Series}} expansion in [[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]].

== Information ==
'''Paradox Drive''' is the fourth themed booster pack of the {{TCGP|B Series}} released through [[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]. It introduces {{TCGP|Ancient}} and {{TCGP|Future}} cards to the game, which revolve primarily around the [[Paradox Pokémon]] introduced in {{g|Scarlet and Violet}}. The mechanics were first introduced in the [[Pokémon Trading Card Game]]'s {{TCG|Paradox Rift}} expansion.

