== Offering rates ==
The following table outlines the offering rates for each individual card in the Paradox Drive booster pack.

The probability of each type of pack appearing is as follows:
* Regular pack - 94.711%
* Regular pack + 1 card - 5.238%
* Rare pack - 0.050%

In regular packs with a bonus card, the card inclusion rates for the first five cards are the same as those for regular packs without a bonus card.

{{Rar/TCGP|Shiny|1}} and {{Rar/TCGP|Shiny|2}} rarity cards are only available as bonus cards.

